data.description: Great place to call home in the heart of Hendersonville! Owner has lived in the community for 12 years and loves the convenience and comfort of the condo.  Primary bedroom down.  2 bedrooms upstairs with full bath.  And large walk in storage space at top of steps. Kitchen has tile floor.  Ceramic tile in upstairs bathroom.  Lots of closets.  Professional Photos coming soon! Swimming pool across the street.  Cost is separate from HOA fee for its use.  Woodburning fireplace.  Fenced area at deck for privacy.   Few steps to the centrally located mailbox.
